title: Exception thrown when exporting data from table containing highlight/map
description: Exception is thrown when trying to export data from the attached report.
OB: An exception is thrown when exporting data from a table that contains a highlight rule and a map rule in a group row.
EB: No exception should be thrown when exporting data from a table that contains a highlight rule and a map rule in a group row.
SR:
To reproduce the issue, please follow these steps:
1. Add a table that has a group, a highlight rule, and a map rule in the group row.
2. Preview the attached report.
3. Export the data from the table.
